name: mother of mountain
description:
Semeru, mother of mountain. The highest mountain on the island of Java, Indonesia. had woken up from a long slumber. the damage it inflicts will be proportional to the fertility to come. Amen.

This work is part of a charity to help victims of the natural disaster from Mount Semeru eruption, every sale in the first market will be 100% donated to the victims, through @clubsewonNFT #TezosforSemeru #Tezos4Semeru
